  "content": "\n \n \n  <section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\">\n   <p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px;border-top: 2px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right: 3px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom: 2px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-style: none;border-left-color: rgb(250, 105, 105);color: var(--weui-FG-1);outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;border-radius: 0px;background: none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(247, 247, 247, 0.97);width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow: auto;visibility: visible;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0em;word-spacing: 0em;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima, PingFangSC-regular, serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px; text-align: left; --theme-color: #4299e1;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;blockquote&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;editId&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;nickname&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;from&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px;border-top: 2px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right: 3px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom: 2px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-style: none;border-left-color: rgb(250, 105, 105);color: var(--weui-FG-1);outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;border-radius: 0px;background: none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(247, 247, 247, 0.97);width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow: auto;visibility: visible;&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：InternLM、Qwen 等 LLM</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(128, 128, 128);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 0em;word-spacing: 0em;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima, PingFangSC-regular, serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px; text-align: left; --theme-color: #4299e1;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;blockquote&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;editId&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;nickname&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;authorName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;from&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px;border-top: 2px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-right: 3px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-bottom: 2px none rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-left-style: none;border-left-color: rgb(250, 105, 105);color: var(--weui-FG-1);outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;border-radius: 0px;background: none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(247, 247, 247, 0.97);width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow: auto;visibility: visible;&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">每周一览热门论文版，顶会投稿选题不迷惘。快来看看由「机智流」和「ModelScope」社区推荐的上周「多模态」方向的热门论文吧！</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong>Unified Reward Model for Multimodal Understanding and Generation&nbsp;</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/124332</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">简要介绍：由复旦大学、上海AI实验室等机构提出了首个统一多模态理解和生成的奖励模型UnifiedReward。该工作构建了大规模人类偏好数据集，包含图像和视频生成/理解任务，并利用该模型进行自动构建高质量偏好对数据，最终通过DPO优化视觉模型。实验结果表明，联合学习评估多样化视觉任务可以带来显著的相互益处。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/91cb8198-b131-48e7-5646-b6482d325500/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 562px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/P0Ka1WNRwjVj4RqT3HhpPGvwucNvFjicibXPlqe0XlwLiciab1ib87JiapTyicMOzODSqzAu96JxsWa5DcMhhWXWyrd9g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"672\" data-cropy1=\"11.95729537366548\" data-cropy2=\"425.6797153024911\" data-imgfileid=\"100018096\" data-ratio=\"0.6175595238095238\" data-w=\"672\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/91cb8198-b131-48e7-5646-b6482d325500/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong>GoT: Unleashing Reasoning Capability of Multimodal Large Language Model for Visual Generation and Editing</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/126628</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：提出了Generation Chain-of-Thought (GoT)，这是一种将推理能力融入视觉生成和编辑的新范式。该工作将常规的文本到图像生成和编辑转变为推理引导框架，分析语义关系和空间排列。研究团队构建了包含900万样本的大规模GoT数据集，并开发了一个统一框架，整合了Qwen2.5-VL的推理能力和扩散模型的生成能力。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b8c16f54-132f-46a2-9553-507203f90b00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018095\" data-ratio=\"0.7425925925925926\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b8c16f54-132f-46a2-9553-507203f90b00/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>Taking Notes Brings Focus? Towards Multi-Turn Multimodal Dialogue Learning</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/125186</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：该研究介绍了MMDiag，一个多轮多模态对话数据集，通过精心设计的规则和GPT辅助生成，特点是问题之间、问题与图像之间以及不同图像区域之间的强相关性。同时提出了DiagNote，一个具备多模态定位和推理能力的MLLM，包含两个相互作用的模块(Deliberate和Gaze)，在多轮对话中执行思维链和注释。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7ab5c1e-711e-4daa-541a-901972ff6d00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018094\" data-ratio=\"1.1502347417840375\" data-w=\"639\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7ab5c1e-711e-4daa-541a-901972ff6d00/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>R1-Omni: Explainable Omni-Multimodal Emotion Recognition with Reinforcing Learning</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/124176</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：这项工作首次将可验证奖励强化学习(RLVR)应用于全模态大型语言模型用于情感识别，这是一项视觉和音频模态都起关键作用的任务。研究利用RLVR优化Omni模型，在三个关键方面显著提升其性能：推理能力、情感识别准确性和泛化能力。这种方法不仅提高了模型在分布内数据上的整体性能，还在分布外数据集评估中展示了更强的鲁棒性。</span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>VisualPRM: An Effective Process Reward Model for Multimodal Reasoning</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/126372</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：由清华大学、上海AI实验室等机构提出了VisualPRM，一个拥有8B参数的多模态过程奖励模型，它通过Best-of-N评估策略显著提升了现有多模态大语言模型的推理能力。该模型改进了三种类型、四种不同规模的MLLM的推理性能，即使应用于InternVL2.5-78B这样的高能力模型，也在七项多模态推理基准上获得了5.9点的提升。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d1b6f3d6-5318-4518-30f0-828524005600/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018093\" data-ratio=\"0.5230125523012552\" data-w=\"717\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d1b6f3d6-5318-4518-30f0-828524005600/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>UniF^2ace: Fine-grained Face Understanding and Generation with Unified Multimodal Models</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/125793</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：研究提出了UniF^2ace，这是第一个专为精细人脸理解和生成设计的统一多模态模型(UMM)。该模型通过两种互补的扩散技术和两级专家混合架构，在特制的数据集上进行训练。团队构建了大规模人脸数据集UniF^2ace-130K，包含13万图像-文本对和100万问答对，涵盖广泛的人脸属性，并建立了离散扩散分数匹配和掩码生成模型之间的理论联系。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/395c8a60-ace9-40ef-597a-b6a12aa80200/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018099\" data-ratio=\"0.6075949367088608\" data-w=\"711\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/395c8a60-ace9-40ef-597a-b6a12aa80200/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>4D LangSplat: 4D Language Gaussian Splatting via Multimodal Large Language Models</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/126311</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：这项工作提出了4D LangSplat，一种学习4D语言场的方法，以便在动态场景中处理时间敏感或时间无关的开放词汇查询。该方法绕过了从视觉特征学习语言场的传统途径，而是直接从多模态大语言模型(MLLM)生成的对象级视频描述文本中学习。研究提出了多模态对象级视频提示方法，生成详细、时间一致的高质量描述，并使用大语言模型将这些描述编码为高质量句子嵌入。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018100\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/97e10473-5925-492b-641d-351c9b6b4200/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/97e10473-5925-492b-641d-351c9b6b4200/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>Vision-R1: Incentivizing Reasoning Capability in Multimodal Large Language Models</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/124832</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：受DeepSeek-R1-Zero成功通过强化学习(RL)激发LLM推理能力的启发，该研究探索了如何利用RL提升多模态大语言模型(MLLM)的推理能力。研究者提出了Vision-R1，通过利用现有MLLM和DeepSeek-R1通过模态桥接和数据过滤构建了20万多模态思维链数据集作为冷启动初始化数据，并提出了渐进思维抑制训练(PTST)策略来减轻冷启动后过度思考的优化挑战。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/30fd6690-d487-4156-e6e3-3413f0b01700/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018101\" data-ratio=\"0.412962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/30fd6690-d487-4156-e6e3-3413f0b01700/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>VisualWebInstruct: Scaling up Multimodal Instruction Data through Web Search</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/126288</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：研究团队提出了VisualWebInstruct，一种利用搜索引擎创建多样化高质量数据集的新方法，涵盖数学、物理、金融、化学等多个学科。从精心挑选的3万种子图像开始，通过Google图像搜索识别包含类似图像的网站，收集并处理了来自70万唯一URL源的HTML。通过内容提取、过滤和合成管道，构建了约90万问答对的数据集，其中40%为视觉QA对，其余为文本QA对。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/833eef62-24b5-452e-5154-6762d9cc9a00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-type=\"jpeg\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100018097\" data-ratio=\"0.6954732510288066\" data-w=\"729\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/833eef62-24b5-452e-5154-6762d9cc9a00/public\"></span></p>\n    <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em auto;padding-right: 0.2em;padding-left: 0.2em;outline: 0px;font-size: 1.2em;display: table;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);background: var(--themeColor);text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><strong>OmniMamba: Efficient and Unified Multimodal Understanding and Generation via State Space Models</strong></span></h2>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">论文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">https://modelscope.cn/papers/125368</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">简要介绍：由华中科技大学等机构提出了OmniMamba，这是首个基于线性架构的多模态生成模型，通过统一的下一个令牌预测范式同时生成文本和图像。该模型充分利用Mamba-2的高计算和内存效率，将其功能从文本生成扩展到多模态生成。为解决现有统一模型的数据效率问题，提出了两项关键创新：解耦词汇表来引导特定模态生成，以及用于参数高效适应的任务特定LoRA。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:justify;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 1.5em 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: hsl(var(--foreground));line-height: 2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\">核心图片：&nbsp;<img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100018098\" data-ratio=\"0.5768518518518518\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58e10a7a-717c-4901-5d63-8c408803b400/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0.5em auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;width: 661px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/58e10a7a-717c-4901-5d63-8c408803b400/public\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin: 8px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;\">-- 完 --</span></p>\n    <section data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;background-position:0% 0%;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-clip:border-box;word-break:break-word;width:auto;font-family:Georgia, PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;background-origin:padding-box;padding-right:10px;text-align:left;\">\n     <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;padding: 10px 20px;border-width: 1px 3px 1px 4px;border-top-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;border-color: rgb(250, 212, 163);border-radius: 0px;background-attachment: scroll, scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(254, 255, 232, 0.7) 0%, rgba(241, 232, 255, 0.7) 100%), none;background-position: 0% 0%, 0% center;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow: auto;\">\n      <section style=\"padding-top:12px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:14px;line-height:2em;\">\n       <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">欢迎在「机智流」公众号后台回复「cc」，加入机智流大模型交流群，与我们一起探索 AI 与人类潜能的未来，一起共赴 AI 浪潮！</span></strong></span>\n      </section>\n     </blockquote>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin: 8px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\">\n       <mp-common-profile data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机智流\" data-alias=\"SmartFlowAI\" data-index=\"0\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/P0Ka1WNRwjVPibwF5B9Wfe9R1nMpsS505LjPicMQw6mm7ZOsxlu8fPC8uk37sam3QPYf5r61clwGnFiaquLTupcJA/300?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=19\" data-signature=\"共赴 AI 时代浪潮~\" data-id=\"Mzg2NzU4MDgzMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-origin_num=\"448\" data-biz_account_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile>\n      </section></span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "推荐了上周多模态方向的十篇热门论文，涵盖多模态理解、生成、推理、人脸处理以及数据集构建等多个方面。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "推荐了上周多模态方向的十篇热门论文，涵盖多模态理解、生成、推理、人脸处理以及数据集构建等多个方面。",
  "summary": "文章总结并推荐了上周在多模态领域发表的十篇热门论文。这些论文涵盖了多模态理解与生成、视觉生成与编辑、多模态对话学习、情感识别、推理能力提升、人脸理解与生成、4D 语言场学习、以及多模态数据集构建等多个研究方向。这些研究由复旦大学、上海 AI 实验室、清华大学等机构的研究团队完成。每篇论文都附有链接和简要介绍，例如，GoT 论文构建了包含 900 万样本的大规模 GoT 数据集，方便读者快速了解其核心内容和创新点。整体来看，这些研究代表了多模态领域的前沿进展，对相关领域的研究人员具有一定的参考价值。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "统一多模态奖励模型可提升视觉任务性能",
      "explanation": "UnifiedReward 通过联合学习评估多样化视觉任务，构建大规模人类偏好数据集，显著提升了模型在图像和视频生成 / 理解任务中的表现。"
    },
    {
      "point": "推理引导框架增强视觉生成和编辑能力",
      "explanation": "GoT 将推理能力融入视觉生成和编辑，通过分析语义关系和空间排列，将常规任务转变为推理引导框架，提升了生成质量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "VisualPRM 通过 Best-of-N 评估策略显著提升了现有多模态大语言模型的推理能力",
      "explanation": "VisualPRM 是一个拥有 8B 参数的多模态过程奖励模型，通过 Best-of-N 评估策略显著提升了现有多模态大语言模型的推理能力，即使应用于 InternVL2.5-78B 这样高能力模型，也在七项多模态推理基准上获得了 5.9 点的提升。"
    },
    {
      "point": "强化学习可有效提升 MLLM 的推理能力",
      "explanation": "Vision-R1 受 DeepSeek-R1 启发，利用强化学习提升多模态大语言模型的推理能力，通过模态桥接和数据过滤构建数据集进行训练。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "联合学习评估多样化视觉任务可以带来显著的相互益处。",
    "该工作将常规的文本到图像生成和编辑转变为推理引导框架，分析语义关系和空间排列。",
    "这项工作首次将可验证奖励强化学习 (RLVR) 应用于全模态大型语言模型用于情感识别。"
